      "beat_id": "B04",
      "t_start": 31.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 13.0,
      "narration_text": "Lab A's density matrix: half the time |0⟩, half the time |1⟩. That is a diagonal matrix with one-half on every diagonal entry — the identity divided by two.",
