      "beat_id": "B07",
      "t_start": 62.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 14.0,
      "narration_text": "Every qubit state lives on or inside the Bloch ball. Pure states sit on the surface. Mixed states live in the interior. The maximally mixed state — identity over two — sits at the exact center, with Bloch vector zero.",
